CBRE is delighted to exclusively offer 26-28 Hargreaves Street, Huntingdale to the market for lease. 

This unique opportunity gives an end user the opportunity establish themselves in Huntingdale’s tightly held commercial and industrial precinct. 

Property highlights include:

+ 3,575 sqm* total building area
+ 3,083 sqm* warehouse area
+ 492 sqm* office and mezzanine areas
+ 12m* internal warehouse clearance
+ Three (3) overhead gantry cranes ranging from 5 to 15 tonnes
+ 400 amps of power
+ 16 on-site car spaces
+ Three separate street frontages (Hargreaves Street, Clifford Street and Shafton Street)
+ Industrial 1 zoning (IN1Z)

Location highlights include:

+ North Road – 250m*
+ Huntingdale Train Station – 650m*
+ Princes Highway – 1.1km*
+ Monash Freeway (M1) – 3km*
+ Melbourne CBD – 16km*

*approx.

CBRE is excited to exclusively offer, for lease, Part 60 Fenton Street, Huntingdale.
 
This property is prominently located in the heart of Huntingdale’s industrial precinct, situated just 20km* from the CBD and in proximity to major arterial roads: Princes Highway (650m*), Monash Freeway (3km*) & North Road (290m*).

Property Features: 
+ Single story office area of 300sqm*
+ Mid-clearance warehousing of 9,926sqm*
+ Total building area of 10,226sqm*
+ Total land area of 15,000sqm*
+ 2 Roller shutter doors
+ High power supply
+ Abundance of on-site carparking 
+ Ability to retain racking (subject to negotiation)
+ Available within 1 month of commitment

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact CBRE’s Lachlan Ferguson, Stephen Adgemis & Sasan Misaghian. All inspections must be booked in advance.

*approximate
